LightSpeed,is,a,point,of,sale,system,for,retailers,It,offers,interactive,solutions,and,management,of,retail,concerns,Single,or,multi,store,operations,can,be,viewed,from,a,streamlined,interface,Inventory,purchasing,and,other,backend,operations,can,be,handled,through,LightSpeed,as,well,Developers,must,pay,to,register,for,API,access,and,documentation